# ===========================================================================
# agentrt-linux（AirymaxOS）管理仓 .gitignore
# 策略：非必要不追踪。各叶子仓自行维护 .gitignore
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 默认忽略所有
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 管理仓必要文件（白名单）
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
!.gitignore
!.gitmodules
!.github/
!.github/**
!CODEOWNERS
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!LICENSE
!MAINTAINERS
!Makefile
!NOTICE
!README.md
!README_zh.md
!SECURITY.md
!.editorconfig
!.clang-format
!scripts/
!ssot-registry.yaml
!tools/
